{"tid":672462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[天倫樂調遷計劃]買沙田公屋/居屋,可唔可以叫住屯門公屋既父母申請調遷來沙田住","createTime":"2018-05-21T04:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T04:15:56.000Z","uid":66701,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1a0ca36b617bc3cb1c35545a308d4e7cd59e551e","tid":672462,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T04:34:41.000Z","msg":"[天倫樂調遷計劃]<br />\n<br />\n如果我買沙田公屋/居屋,可唔可以叫住屯門公屋既父母申請調遷來沙田住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條件 - 我: 沙田公屋戶主(用綠表買入的2手公屋)<br />\n          父母: 2老過60, 住緊屯門公屋 (租)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d9e3fbd57bec19f00bb73268441e3ece010330","tid":672462,"uid":66701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T06:02:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"53c6f0e057c5c3c55e16fddf2a4cbe0ab1d36356","tid":672462,"uid":135957,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T03:19:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7faaa74f9b000613499cd89d50ca4d78e63fbbfa","tid":672462,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T03:20:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74c84da305861d4dab39ec2f26dc616653e028d6","tid":672462,"uid":90152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T03:45:24.000Z","msg":"天倫樂應該係兩個household都係房署租戶先可以申請<br />\n<br />\n如果爸爸媽媽有需要有人照顧<br />\n同時又有能力自己住而唔需要照顧者同住<br />\n同時又有醫生推薦<br />\n調遷後有明顯的正面影響<br />\n先至有機會申請到特別調遷<br />\n申請階段你需要來回申請調遷公屋住戶所屬的綜合家庭服務中心<br />\n該屋邨房屋事務處<br />\n醫院<br />\n去處理申請文件<br />\n<br />\n即使申請成功亦要該地區有空置而適合大小的單位<br />\n才可獲得編配<br />\n<br />\n我個人認為你需要考慮以下因素：<br />\n1.父母在原住地的社區支援及鄰里關係<br />\n2.父母能否適應調遷後的生活（所有服務設施衣食住行都唔同）<br />\n3.父母的醫療服務安排（如適用）<br />\n4.你一星期需要來回父母家的次數<br />\n5.沙田區內交通可以好麻煩，例如你住馬鞍山，父母調遷派去新田圍或者水泉澳，唔見得時間上相差好多<br />\n6.係你一廂情願定係雙方都願意，始終要適應新環境唔係容易<br />\n7.申請原因係唔係真係説服到房署同社會福利署，由「新界」調去「拓展市區」係講緊用左一個「拓展市區」預留比重建市區公屋住戶，緊急調遷，有特殊原因嘅住戶（如子女上學需要）嘅單位"},{"pid":"ec316bc503347a568334fb117f4801f20758c4ff","tid":672462,"uid":70174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53c6f0e057c5c3c55e16fddf2a4cbe0ab1d36356","tid":672462,"uid":135957,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T03:19:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T04:15:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}